title: Dhol
subTitle: Four lazy friends want to make easy money and aim to marry a rich girl. Their plan backfires after they meet Ritu and get embroiled with a dangerous criminal.

title: Sau Din Saas Ke
subTitle: Durga marries Prakash, unaware of his mother Bhawani Devi's dominating and abusive nature. She later insists on moving in with his family in order to teach Bhawani Devi a lesson.

title: Judaai
subTitle: Lured by wealth, Kajal asks her husband, Raj, an honest engineer, to get married to Janhvi, the rich daughter of his boss. Little does she know about the problems that await her.

title: Surya Putra Shani Dev
subTitle: Ravi and his wife, Leena, learn about Lord Shanidev's greatness from a village priest while en route to Mumbai. Later, Ravi and Leena's faith is tested when Ravi meets with an accident.

title: Son of Sardaar
subTitle: Jaswinder returns to his hometown to sell a piece of land he owns and falls in love with a young woman only to find out later that her family wants him dead.

title: Chote Sarkar
subTitle: When two cops frame Amar, a businessman, of murdering his uncle, he pretends to be of unsound mind to escape apprehension and find the real murderer.

title: Daag: The Fire
subTitle: Karan, a former soldier, learns that his father committed suicide after being accused of a crime he did not commit. So he sets out to exact revenge on the lawyer who is responsible for his loss.

title: Swarg
subTitle: Krishna worships his master, Sahabji, but circumstances lead to his ouster from the house. He works hard, becomes a powerful man and returns to restore his master's honour.

title: Andolan
subTitle: Adarsh and Aniket are two brothers who study in the same college. However, when they graduate and plan to establish a career, both of them choose different paths and gradually drift apart.

title: Andolan
subTitle: Adarsh and Aniket are two brothers who study in the same college. However, when they graduate and plan to establish a career, both of them choose different paths and gradually drift apart.

title: Qaidi
subTitle: Ravi Verma, a CBI officer, infiltrates the gang of a notorious criminal, Kali, pretending to be him. However, things take a turn when Kali regains his consciousness.

title: Rajoo Dada
subTitle: Rajoo intends to exact revenge on his parents' killers and grows up to be a criminal. However, he needs to join hands with his brother, who is a police officer, to find the culprits.

title: Souten
subTitle: Shyam, a middle-class man, falls in love with a millionaire's daughter and marries her. However, as their relationship starts deteriorating, Shyam finds solace in the company of Radha.

title: Chandni
subTitle: Rohit sets out to find his former lover, whom he leaves due to his accident. When he meets her, he finds out she is engaged to marry her boss.

title: Kyo Kii Main Jhuth Nahin Bolta
subTitle: Raj is a lawyer who finds great success with his countless fibs. However, when his son wishes for his father to stop lying, Raj is magically forced to speak the truth, which lands him in trouble.

title: Dil Ka Rishta
subTitle: Jai, a wealthy businessman in love with Tia, accidentally kills her husband in a car crash. After the accident Tia loses her memory and falls for Jai, who struggles with guilt.

title: Bhagam Bhaag
subTitle: A drama troupe flies to London for a performance. However, things take a tragic turn when three members of their team are falsely accused of murder.

title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fiancé plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.

title: Adventures of Tarzan
subTitle: Ruby ventures into the forest searching for a legendary tribe but encounters Tarzan and falls for him. However, her father and fiancé plot to capture him and sell him to the circus.

title: Inquilaab
subTitle: A politician helps a jobless man become a police officer and then uses him for his nefarious activities. After his wife finds out he is being used as a pawn, she tries to change his ways.

title: Jurmana
subTitle: A flambouyant businessman places a bet with his former college friend to woo their professor's young daughter. However, the bet leads to a series of unexpected consequences.

title: Deewaar
subTitle: Haunted by the past, Vijay turns to crime, while Ravi, his younger brother, becomes an honest police officer. Fate pits them against each other when Ravi is sent to nab Vijay.

title: Aan: Men at Work
subTitle: DCP Hari Om Patnaik, along with his reformed force, takes up the challenge to make Mumbai crime-free. However, things take a turn for the worse when they lose two of their team members.

title: Rishtey
subTitle: A man marries his lover and has a child with her against the wishes of her wealthy father. However, his scheming father-in-law ruins their marriage and leaves to care for his boy by himself.

title: Singham Returns
subTitle: Bajirao Singham, an honest police officer, encounters Babaji, a god-man with connections to high profile politicians, when he investigates the death of an officer from his team.

title: Tridev
subTitle: When an expelled police inspector, an outlaw and a commissioner's son are implicated by a dealer, they unite to seek revenge and prove they are not culprits.

title: Boss
subTitle: Disowned by his father as a boy, Surya seeks protection from a crime boss. When his brother is wrongfully sent to prison, his father begs him to intervene.
